OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMeta told to overhaul      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpolicies over doxxing fears
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Meta's Oversight Board has advised the 
OL,6, social network to change its policy on 
OL,7, allowing the sharing of people's       
OL,8, addresses, even if the information is  
OL,9, considered public.                     
OL,11,FMeta requested the advice last year -  
OL,12,Fthe first time it has asked the board  
OL,13,Fto help define one of its policies.    
OL,15,FIt follows a series of leaks on social 
OL,16,Fmedia of high-profile people's         
OL,17,Faddresses.                             
OL,19,FThis so-called doxxing could cause     
OL,20,Freal-world harms, the board advised.   
